data.description: This large and functional townhome is conveniently located on hwy 17 with close proximity to the interstate, boeing, volvo, shopping, restaurants and entertainment. This home is equipped with 5 bedrooms and 3 full bathrooms, a laundry room, pantry, and loft area, with one bedroom and full bathroom downstairs. At 2,447 square feet, there is room for everyone. Enjoy 2 car garage parking with a spacious driveway, and a screened in patio on the back for entertaining and enjoying family. The amenities center at Cypress Ridge offers something for every member of your family, with everything from a playground and resort-style pool, to picnic areas and workout facilities.
